{Planning human resource management }\plain \f1
\fs22
\cf1
{involves identifying and documenting project roles, responsibilities, and report
ing relationships. The main output of this process is a human resource plan.\par
}\plain \f1
\fs22
\cf1
{\par
}\plain \f1
\fs22
\cf1
\plain \b \f1
\fs22
\cf1
{Acquiring the project team}\plain \f1
\fs22
\cf1
{ involves assigning the needed personnel to work on the project. Key outputs of 
this process are project staff assignments, resource calendars, and project manag
ement plan updates.\par
}\plain \f1
\fs22
\cf1
{\par
}\plain \f1
\fs22
\cf1
\plain \b \f1
\fs22
\cf1
{Developing the project team }\plain \f1
\fs22
\cf1
